{"tid":808959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：不宜向孩子灌輸「玩遊戲是罪惡」的觀念","createTime":"2018-09-06T17:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T02:45:43.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"44154613ae9f12f0efe488dc981bce3e91377007","tid":808959,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"2018/09/06 17:33<br />\n人民日報在發表了《防的是沈迷而非網游》一文後，緊接著又發表了《怎麼玩才健康 玩什麼才恰當》，指出：家長不宜向孩子灌輸「玩遊戲是罪惡」的觀念<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網絡遊戲防沈迷，怎麼做才能有效且長效？專家建議，家長不宜向孩子灌輸「玩遊戲是罪惡」的觀念，而應該幫助孩子提升自制力。遊戲公司除了設置「一鍵禁玩」及「限額消費」等功能，還應該制定方案，使青少年遠離不良內容。社會給予引導、家長言傳身教、遊戲公司開發優質內容、相關部門承擔監管責任，才能形成完整、有效的閉環。"},{"pid":"79170908aeb744ae65bda919fda548235efea123","tid":808959,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrb/html/2018-09/05/nw.D110000renmrb_20180905_1-15.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.people.com.cn%2Frmrb%2Fhtml%2F2018-09%2F05%2Fnw.D110000renmrb_20180905_1-15.htm&d=GWPW7JtnNR0n12GJohEXkTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=17c74f5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://paper.people.com.cn/rmrb/html/2018-09/05/nw.D110000renmrb_20180905_1-15.htm</a>"},{"pid":"baa39aa2213a9e650143cb9ff28ed44096c1ba29","tid":808959,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T20:03:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409182e08797ff990e8834adf5b80165993e5ab4","tid":808959,"uid":80535,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T20:40:35.000Z","msg":"共產黨教人地教仔喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c444a3e166a8f4e4b0be32149e0fdf7fc85cc039","tid":808959,"uid":96743,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T21:33:22.000Z","msg":"打到隻700沈左先 再大手入貨 共狗識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca420708c